tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_nutrition_info (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name STRING,
    age INT,
    weight DECIMAL,
    height DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE nutrition_information (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  meal_time TIMESTAMP,
  calories INT,
  protein FLOAT,
  fat FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Nutrition (
    nutrition_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES Users(user_id),
    calories INT NOT NULL,
    protein INT NOT NULL,
    carbohydrates INT NOT NULL,
    fats INT NOT NULL,
    log_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE MealPlans (
    plan_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES Users(user_id),
    plan_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    plan_description VARCHAR(200),
    start_date DATE NOT NULL,
    end_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Nutrition (
	nutrition_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	user_id INT,
	calories INT,
	protein INT,
	carbs INT,
	fat INT
);

CREATE TABLE Plan (
	plan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	user_id INT,
	plan_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE nutrition_info (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    calorie_count INT,
    protein_count INT,
    carb_count INT,
    fat_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE meals (
    meal_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    plan_id INT,
    meal_name TEXT,
    calories INT,
    proteins INT,
    carbs INT,
    fats INT
);
